description: Horizons Holdings International, Corp. operates as a real estate holding, investment, and development company. It is primarily involved in the acquisition and management of mid-tier vacation properties in Central America and the Caribbean islands. The company was formerly known as Horizon Health International Corp. and changed its name to Horizons Holdings International, Corp. in April 2015. Horizons Holdings International, Corp. was founded in 1969 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
